 "name": "RPlog_S.O.S.",
 "title": "S.O.S.",
 "summary": "Two days after suspicious transmissions were first picked up on a New Republic military frequency, a strained voice breaks through the static again: it is Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard, reporting from the Imperial Star Destroyer Nemesis and pleading for anyone to respond. Going by her codename Canary, the captive ambassador broadcasts her distress call into the void in the desperate hope of rescue. The brief, tense log captures Delgard's lifeline out of Imperial custody and the slim chance that someone is listening.",
